{"tid":196568,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"觀眾口碑太好！7 部成本超低爆賺的電影 這部居然翻了一萬倍票房報酬！","createTime":"2017-04-11T11:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:01:16.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"759ac76e1a4653799c3bd57c44a7870b43f70895","tid":196568,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"萊恩&middot;雷諾斯（Ryan Reynolds）主演的《惡棍英雄：死侍》（Deadpool）去年以超低的 5800 萬美元超級英雄電影預算，即使沒在中國上映，最終還是成功在全球票房收入 7.83 億美元，爆賺的程度讓二十世紀福斯樂開懷。事實上過去也有不少以「小成本、立大功」的知名電影，通常這些電影都是因為第一批觀眾看了之後口碑太好，因而掀起了一波觀影潮，以下我們就為大家來盤點這些小成本卻賺翻的經典之作。<br />\n<br />\n▼2013 年的驚悚電影《國定殺戮日》（The Purge）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64520/58e70ddef40af.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64520%2F58e70ddef40af.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=0bc1a22e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以 300 萬美元的超低成本，收入了 8932 萬美元票房，人類清除計畫的刺激題材大受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n▼2006 年的音樂電影《曾經。愛是唯一》（Once）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64520/58e70ea44df7e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64520%2F58e70ea44df7e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=e5713cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影成本只有 15 萬美元，結果在全球收入 940 萬票房，翻了超過 60 倍，還拿下了一座奧斯卡小金人。<br />\n<br />\n▼2007 年的恐怖電影《靈動：鬼影實錄》（Paranormal Activity）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64520/58e70ff9b35d1.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64520%2F58e70ff9b35d1.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=baa47307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這部驚悚電影創造了令人目瞪口呆的紀錄，劇組僅用了 1.5 萬美元成本拍攝，最終全球票房居然收破 1.93 億美元，翻了一萬倍。<br />\n<br />\n▼1989 年的獨立電影《性、謊言、錄影帶》（Sex, Lies, and Videotape）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64520/58e711681a864.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64520%2F58e711681a864.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=de5d386e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n導演史蒂芬&middot;索德柏的成名作品，以 120 萬美元成本，收入 2470 萬美元票房。<br />\n<br />\n▼1999 年的恐怖電影《厄夜叢林》（The Blair Witch Project）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64520/58e712123708c.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64520%2F58e712123708c.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=162ab8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這部電影已經是恐怖片之中的經典名作，當時以 6 萬美元的成本，收入 1.4 億美元票房。<br />\n<br />\n▼1976 年運動電影《洛基》（Rocky）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64520/58e712ec0b7b9.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64520%2F58e712ec0b7b9.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a3d380f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n席維斯&middot;史特龍的成名之作，《洛基》第一集以 95 萬美元成本拍攝，最終收入 1.17 億美元票房，還橫掃了當年奧斯卡大獎。<br />\n<br />\n▼2004 年的恐怖電影《奪魂鋸》（Saw）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64520/58e70b293620c.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64520%2F58e70b293620c.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=68e8bc3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫子仁開創的《奪魂鋸》經典系列，首集以 120 萬美元的低成本，最終成功收入了 5518 萬美金的票房，更掀起了全球的《奪魂鋸》熱潮，不過可以發現以低成本博高票房，還是恐怖電影的成功率比較高。<br />\n<br />\n▼ 2015 年的警匪電影《赤道》（Helios）<br />\n<img src=\"http://photo.pengpeng.com/pic/201312/16/rxblxuyhwjmjppi1652_original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto.pengpeng.com%2Fpic%2F201312%2F16%2Frxblxuyhwjmjppi1652_original.jpg&h=f26b954c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪的成名之作，《赤道》第一集以 95 萬美元成本拍攝，最終收入 1.17 個千萬億兆京垓秭穰溝澗正載極恆河沙阿僧祇那由他不可思議無量大數美元票房，還橫掃了當年奧斯卡大獎。"},{"pid":"7b7ace192deb897a2d48b3343a250a66a0cb73ff","tid":196568,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"無睇名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed56de654ecc58663b82ec5ed80fd70a7e935c03","tid":196568,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"點解有赤道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf750450525910107c60586e0d72221aea38845","tid":196568,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"又朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e39b55a6f7d19c49f1db5b1946ba6b3261418b","tid":196568,"uid":82661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:16:20.000Z","msg":"唔記得睇名就入左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64887300895d9342def07c657060095d714d9fc0","tid":196568,"uid":8854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28d5bc28f1d3587eccefaf318b04c980c418a63f","tid":196568,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"DIU<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21688dffa8fffe4b4bf9be35eac8b64a2d73a537","tid":196568,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"最終收入 1.17 個千萬億兆京垓秭穰溝澗正載極恆河沙阿僧祇<br />\n即係幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92744840b2b08e1dfdd4672866b5163f72572435","tid":196568,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"<b